    +paste.filter_factory = swift.common.middleware.streaming.streaming:filter_factory

 * upload flowplayer landing page AND movie.mp4 (not included):
    
    swift upload video flowplayer.html movie.mp4

 * set public acl on video container

    swift post video -r .r:*

 * point browser to video player

    http://<swift-all-in-one-ip>:8080/v1/AUTH_test/video/flowplayer.html




